properties.Name: CustomerShipmentMethod
properties.Description:
The customer shipment parameters associated with a customer for the indicated period defined by:

- Shipment Method
- Carrier

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: ShipmentMethodId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment Method.

Columns.Name: CarrierId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Carrier.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated customer shipment method information is defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated customer shipment method information is defined.

Columns.Name: PreferenceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Preference.

Columns.Name: CustomerShipmentMethodNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the associated customer shipment method.
